data.description: Motivated Seller willing to contribute to buyers closing costs! Welcome home to this spacious and inviting 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem!  With three generously sized bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, there's plenty of room for your family to spread out and enjoy their own space. The heart of the home, the family room boasts a charming fireplace, perfect for creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere on those chilly winter evenings. The kitchen is well-equipped with all the modern appliances you need to whip up delicious meals. It's the perfect place to enjoy cooking and entertaining friends and family. The main bedroom is wheelchair accessible, ensuring comfort and convenience. The attached bathroom is designed with accessibility in mind, making daily routines easier.  The fenced backyard offers a nice private space, and you'll also love spending sunny afternoons in the above-ground pool, perfect for cooling off during the summer months. The furnace and AC were replaced approximately 2 years ago, roof was done in approximately 2017 and windows approximately 2010. A two-car garage for your vehicles or extra storage. Proximity to schools, parks, shopping centers, and public transportation. This home truly has it all - a blend of comfort, accessibility, and outdoor enjoyment. Don't miss the chance to make it your own! Schedule a viewing today to experience the magic for yourself. Your dream home awaits!
